1.2 Core Design Principles

```
1. **Quantum Privacy First**: 
   ├─ Patient data encrypted with QKD-generated one-time pads
   ├─ Quantum homomorphic encryption for computation on encrypted data
   └─ Zero-knowledge quantum proofs for data sharing without exposure

2. **Real-time Global Processing**:
   ├─ Distributed quantum AI across 600+ satellite nodes
   ├─ Sub-10ms latency for emergency response
   └─ Continuous health monitoring with quantum pattern recognition

3. **Molecular Precision**:
   ├─ Quantum simulation of biological processes at atomic level
   ├─ Protein folding in minutes vs. years
   ├─ Personalized medicine at molecular resolution
   └─ Quantum control of drug delivery systems

4. **Universal Access**:
   ├─ Global coverage including remote/rural areas via satellite
   ├─ Quantum devices at multiple price points
   ├─ Multilingual quantum interfaces with real-time translation
   └─ Accessibility features built into quantum interfaces
```

