   └─ Nanoscale imaging (quantum plasmonics)
├─ Communication:
   ├─ Quantum body-area network (QBAN) to wearable hub
   ├─ 1550nm quantum-safe optical communication through tissue
   ├─ Data rate: 1Gbps, 24/7 operation
   └─ Lifetime: 10 years (self-recharging)
├─ Processing:
   ├─ On-chip quantum processor (10 qubits for real-time analysis)
   ├─ Edge AI for anomaly detection
   └─ Autonomous emergency signaling
└─ Security:
   ├─ Quantum physical unclonable function (QPUF) for device identity
   ├─ QKD with wearable hub for secure communication
   └─ Tamper-evident quantum seals

Network Architecture:
Patient → 5-20 implantable sensors → Wearable Quantum Hub → Quantum 6G Satellite → Healthcare Cloud
```

