   ├─ Risk: Doctors, patients resistant to quantum technologies
   ├─ Mitigation: Education, demonstration of benefits, gradual introduction
   ├─ Design: Human-centered quantum healthcare interfaces
   └─ Incentives: Align rewards with quantum healthcare adoption

